The paladin as he grows in skill, learns to summon forth a special horse<br>
and fight mounted.<br>
<br>
Good-aligned Mounts<br>
Clydesdale - Apple<br>
Paso Fino - Bale of Hay<br>
Paint Horse - Lump of Sugar<br>
Morgan - Stalk of Wild Wheat<br>
Saglawi - Block of Salt<br>
Haflinger - Carrot<br>
Appaloosa - Stalk of Straw<br>
Fox Trotter - Handful of Oats<br>
Kuhaylan - Blade of Grass<br>
Muniqi - Ear of Corn<br>
<br>
